      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.themes.Item.cmnIJbltlo1d5oZn]{Prisoner}</p>\n<p>While incarcerated, you honed your skill at concealing contraband from the guards and other prisoners. You gain a +2 bonus to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.qVEW9HjXQN0ok879]{Sleight of Hand} checks to hide an object on your body, and the +4 bonus to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.gZlg2ZKze0erNLmP]{Perception} a person would normally receive from observing you or searching your body is reduced by 2. In addition, you can retrieve a hidden object as a move action rather than a standard action.</p>"
